data.description: Welcome to your Dream Home with absolutely No Restrictions located on approx 2.06 Acres! This Stunning Property offers a unique blend of spacious living and versatile outdoor amenities, making it the perfect retreat for those seeking a balance of work and play. Situated on a corner lot. Let's start with the impressive 24x40x16 shop on a concrete slab. This shop is a hobbyist's dream, featuring an awning for outdoor workspace, a convenient restroom, and two bay doors (14x12 and 8x8) providing easy access for your projects. With all-electric capabilities and exterior air compressor hookups, this space is ready to accommodate your creative endeavors. Plus, there are RV hookups for your convenience and a gated entrance for added security. For those who love the great outdoors, this property has it all. The acre and a half of land is fenced, providing ample space for your furry friends to roam freely in the dog run, while the chicken coop and fenced garden are perfect for cultivating your green thumb. And when it's time to relax, you'll appreciate the above-ground swimming pool and hot tub with a deck. As you step inside the main residence, you'll be greeted by a welcoming wrap-around porch, a place where you can unwind and enjoy the cool breeze. The interior is equally impressive, featuring three bedrooms and two and a half baths. The vaulted ceilings create an airy atmosphere, and the spacious layout includes a game room, office, mudroom with entry/exit door, and walk-in pantry. With walk-in closets, storage space won't be an issue. Recent upgrades add value and peace of mind to your new home. The dishwasher and refrigerator have been recently replaced, and one of the AC units has been upgraded as well, while the other has received professional maintenance in the spring. The roof, carpets, and floors were all installed in 2018, ensuring a modern and well-maintained interior. Don't miss your chance to make this remarkable property your forever home!
